<figure class="image-placeholder"><img alt="20200104_m_pin_duo_duo_-fu_mu_peng_you_quan__Large.png" src="https://www.zaobao.com/sites/default/files/inline_images/20201227/20200104_m_pin_duo_duo_-fu_mu_peng_you_quan__Large.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><figcaption>拼多多也附上死者父母的截图，强调公司一直与死者父母保持联系，尊重家属意愿，没有公布这一消息。（互联网）</figcaption></figure>
